WEBVTT

1
00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:05.640 
邓肯·赫茨
Duncan Herz?

2
00:02:05.930 --> 00:02:06.840 
那个披萨大王
The pizza king?

3
00:02:08.590 --> 00:02:10.180 
他又要离婚了吗
Is he getting divorced again?

4
00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:12.270 
不是  他被一个剧给嘲讽了
No. He was satirized in a play,

5
00:02:12.270 --> 00:02:14.330 
他想以诽谤的名义提出控告
and now he wants to sue for defamation.

6
00:02:14.340 --> 00:02:15.680 
告诉他看开点
Tell him to let it go.

7
00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:19.280 
你不搭理  自然就没人嘲了
Satire just disappears if you don't give it any oxygen.

8
00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.040 
没人喜欢看嘲讽
Everybody hates satire.

9
00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:23.570 
不幸的是  我认识那个编剧
Unfortunately, I recognized the playwright.

10
00:02:23.660 --> 00:02:26.430 
他去年在这儿工作  是名律师
He worked here last year, as an associate.

11
00:02:26.740 --> 00:02:27.540 
谁
Who?

12
00:02:28.340 --> 00:02:29.920 
贾马尼·詹金斯
Jumaane Jenkins.

13
00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:32.590 
他原来叫亚纶·诺斯
Oh, but his name used to be Alan North.

14
00:02:34.230 --> 00:02:36.270 
因为嗑药被我们炒了的那个
The one we fired for drug use.

